	<section class="content-section">
		<h2>Our Cosmetic Dental Services</h2>
		<p>We believe that cosmetic enhancements should look entirely natural and complement your unique facial features.</p>
		<ul>
			<li><strong>Professional Teeth Whitening:</strong> Achieve a noticeably brighter smile safely and quickly. Unlike over-the-counter strips, our professional-grade whitening treatments penetrate deep into the enamel to lift stubborn stains caused by coffee, tea, wine, or smoking, without causing extreme sensitivity.</li>
			<li><strong>Porcelain Veneers:</strong> Thin, custom-crafted porcelain shells permanently bonded to the front of your teeth. Veneers are the ultimate solution for fixing chipped, severely discolored, slightly crooked, or unevenly spaced teeth, giving you a flawless "Hollywood" smile.</li>
			<li><strong>Dental Bonding:</strong> A quick, cost-effective alternative to veneers for repairing minor chips or gaps using a tooth-colored composite resin.</li>
			<li><strong>Complete Smile Makeovers:</strong> A comprehensive, customized plan that may combine several treatments (such as Invisalign, whitening, and veneers) to completely rejuvenate your smile.</li>
